-:RELEASE INFO:-

Pattam Pole is a 2013 Malayalam romantic film scripted by Girish Kumar, directed by renowned cinematographer Alagappan, who makes his directorial debut, and produced by Karunakaran under the banner of Carlton Films. The film tracks the relationship between a Brahmin youth, Karthik, and a Christian girl, Riya. Dulquer Salmaan plays the role of Karthik and new face Malavika Mohan, daughter of Bollywood cinematographer K. U. Mohanan, appears as Riya. Archana Kavi, Anoop Menon, Lalu Alex, Jayaprakash, Seetha, Leema Babu, Shraddha Gokul, Nandhu and Ilavarasu play supporting roles. The film commenced its production in June 2013 and was mainly shot from Alappuzha in Kerala and Kumbakonam in Tamil Nadu.
